<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: composite_group_shape_aspect
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_group_shape_aspect">
<note> The local rules for this entity have not been fully updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

A <b>composite_group_shape_aspect</b> is a  <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> that implements the
ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_group_shape_element"/>.
</p></ext_description>

